1. *Sos* je odličan dodatak testeninama. (The *sauce* is an excellent addition to pasta.)
2. Ne znam kako da napravim dobar *sos*. (I don't know how to make a good *sauce*.)
3. Za ovaj recept treba nam malo *sosa*. (We need a little bit of *sauce* for this recipe.)
4. Ovaj *sos* je preljut za mene. (This *sauce* is too spicy for me.)
5. Pogledaj koliko je *sosa* ostalo u tegli. (Look how much *sauce* is left in the jar.)
6. Da li ste probali ovaj specijalni *sos* za roštilj? (Have you tried this special *sauce* for barbecue?)
7. *Sos* od paradajza je jedan od najpopularnijih u Italiji. (Tomato *sauce* is one of the most popular in Italy.)
8. Dodajte malo *sosa* ako vam je jelo suvo. (Add a little bit of *sauce* if your meal is dry.)
9. Nažalost, *sos* je prosuo po stolu. (Unfortunately, the *sauce* spilled on the table.)
10. Nemoj da zaboraviš da kupiš *sos* za pohovane šnicle. (Don't forget to buy *sauce* for breaded schnitzels.)